{"tid":1471734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月13日晚兩個時段影登機牌發現","createTime":"2019-08-14T10:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:10:50.000Z","uid":224929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f301393557355336d917d444e3846cd1dc3fd47","tid":1471734,"uid":224929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:53:04.000Z","msg":"由於見到有人話機管局假扮取消航班，所以岩岩翻睇琴晚影既登機牌有以下發現，發現左機管局真係扮取消航班，對旅客造成損失，以及意圖將責任歸咎示威者，造成群眾鬥群眾既下三流手段。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocNjGmV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocNjGmV.png&h=68791bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖為8月13日 18:48 影既登機牌<br />\n<br />\n留意左二排2025及2030 去新加坡/吉隆坡/馬尼拉，三架幾當時係cancel左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWYyLPo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWYyLPo.png&h=12099579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上圖為8月13日 19:51 影既最左排登機牌<br />\n<br />\n上面提到既三班機已變成boarding &amp; boarding soon<br />\n<br />\n以下附上由「機管局」手機app 我的航班所顯示關於以上三班聯營航班的航班編號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NfqYcxz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNfqYcxz.png&h=fc3066e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fzz2EcA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzz2EcA.png&h=57c2329d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X6NLBZf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX6NLBZf.png&h=f55a0110&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9522b2281c2ea436107c29bebe61238bf026d34d","tid":1471734,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:53:49.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><